---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const contactEmail = 'bingham.stuart@gmail.com';
const lastUpdated = 'July 16, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Stuart Bingham"
  description="How stuartbingham.net handles your information: no analytics, no tracking cookies, and messages used only to reply to you."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16">
    <p class="kicker mb-3">LEGAL</p>
    <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mono-label mb-10 text-text-muted">[ last updated: {lastUpdated} ]</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-text">
      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-h3">The short version</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose">
          This is a personal portfolio site. There are no ads, no analytics, and no tracking.
          The only information collected is what you choose to send when you contact me, and it
          is used only to reply to you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-h3">Information you provide</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose">
          If you reach out through the contact form, the chat widget, email, or phone, I receive
          what you send: your name, contact details, and message. The contact form opens your own
          email app, so your message travels as ordinary email. Chat messages are delivered to me
          as notifications so I can respond.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-h3">Information collected automatically</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose">
          None by this site. There are no analytics scripts and no tracking cookies. Your theme
          preference (dark, light, or party mode) is stored in your own browser's local storage
          and never leaves your device. The site is served by Cloudflare, which processes standard
          server logs (like IP addresses) to deliver and protect the site; see Cloudflare's privacy
          policy for details.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-h3">Data sharing</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose">
          Your information is never sold or shared, other than the service providers involved in
          delivering messages (for example, email and SMS carriers).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-h3">Your rights</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose">
          Want a message you sent me corrected or deleted? Just ask and it's done.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-h3">Changes</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose">
          If this policy changes, the update appears on this page with a new date above.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-h3">Contact</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose">
          Questions about any of this: <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`} class="font-medium text-accent-text underline-offset-4 hover:underline">{contactEmail}</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
